ActCanadian Centre for Occupational Health and Safety Act
PrecisAppointment of SHELLEY ANNE ROWAN of Halifax, Nova Scotia, to be a governor of the Council of the Canadian Centre for Occupational Health and Safety, being the nominee of the Lieutenant Governor in Council of the Province of Nova Scotia, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years.
